So sad to hear of the passing of the legendary Peter Lindbergh. I feel lucky to have worked with him just a couple of months ago.. we laughed and chatted about his plans for the summer.. he was a master of his craft but it was his sense of humour, his warmth and kindness that stayed with me. Sending love and condolences to his family 💔
